yTime":"2019-08-10T00:37:08.000Z","msg":"比多個推你"},{"pid":"fec17986ac45e87063366a0012a951cc260aa313","tid":1438681,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:39:16.000Z","msg":"如果慣咗舒服 未必想回歸危險"},{"pid":"ab2fb004bc99211ef5801882eeedd20899aefade","tid":1438681,"uid":10691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:40:12.000Z","msg":"我唔建議勇武主動攻擊 但打一定要還手<br />\n而家外面個風向 感覺上想勇武收皮咁<br />\n我唔想佢地俾人當condom 我地都係手足<br />\n你地要記得 佢地係保護香港嘅香港人黎㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"503dd019d5410e5d71d0f97bb0d0b53b53822216","tid":1438681,"uid":10691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:43:30.000Z","msg":"而且不得不說 和理非亦都係史前進化到多元化 係有用嘅 但真係要雙管齊下 <br />\n如果唔係政府只會noted and thank<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記得五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n勿忘初心</span>"},{"pid":"7783ebcc4d8e61da4bf659aa3a45b61ac4caf941","tid":1438681,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:45:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d07007640d6032512a23e9bf4aa65bc9ae24a87","tid":1438681,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:45:45.000Z","msg":"你以為唔攻人哋就無時間睇會唔會太天真，隔嚟，我俾佢5000防暴，扣除文職仲有一萬幾千人，而且隔嚟都有post話開到200蚊個鐘ot叫狗睇片"},{"pid":"97631c87518c8d7186eea42c5f90ae2c88cb8e00","tid":1438681,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:46:21.000Z","msg":"勇武繼續上！<br />\n文宣繼續做！<br />\n和理非繼續靜坐遊行集會！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山！</span></span><br />\n香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"60bcc59eb631ade7208615fd44a236eb0ca03b4e","tid":1438681,"uid":10691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d07007640d6032512a23e9bf4aa65bc9ae24a87","tid":1438681,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:45:45.000Z","msg":"你以為唔攻人哋就無時間睇會唔會太天真，隔嚟，我俾佢5000防暴，扣除文職仲有一萬幾千人，而且隔嚟都有post話開到200蚊個鐘ot叫狗睇片"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:49